com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface ReadCreditMemoRequestsService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultReadCreditMemoRequestsService

    public interface ReadCreditMemoRequestsService

    This service enables external applications to integrate with read methods for processing credit memo requests in SAP S/4HANA Cloud. It enables you to retrieve credit memo requests in an API call.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_CREDIT_MEMO_REQUEST_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Credit Memo Request Integration (SAP_COM_0158)
    Scope Items:Credit Memo Processing (1EZ)
